# Bug Report: Password reset email not sent after valid email submission

## Description:
Forgot password with valid email, not is received link for instruction on email.

## Pre-conditions:
User is on the “Forgot Password” page.

## Steps to reproduce:
1. Navigate to facebook.com  
2. Type “Mario Mladenov” into the “Username” field.  
3. Type “PasswordStrong” into the “Password” field.  
4. Click on “Forgot password”  
5. Submit with valid email

## Actual Result:
No reset email received.

## Expected Result:
User receives password reset email and sees confirmation message.

## Severity:
Major

## Environment:
Google Chrome Version: 137.0.7151.56 (64-bit)
